          "description": "Some Philips models have audio sync issues with DTS passthrough, particularly with older receivers. Audio may be slightly out of sync.",
          "severity": "warning",
          "codecs": ["dts", "dtshd"],
          "workaround": "Use AC-3 or E-AC-3 passthrough instead, or enable audio decoding to PCM",
          "resolved": false
        },
        {
          "id": "philips-saphi-mkv-hdr",
          "title": "HDR Playback Issues in MKV on Saphi OS",
          "description": "Some Philips TVs running Saphi OS have issues playing HDR content in MKV containers. Android TV models generally handle this better.",
